            <p>This website is aimed at all foreigners interested in learning about Finnish language and culture.</p>
            <p>A growing interest in Finland has motivated various content creators to produce valuable information for foreigners. Because we value such dedicated work, and also truly believe in the power of diversity brought by foreigners to this unique country, we decided to create a page where all such awesome content could be displayed in an organized manner, to facilitate everyone's access to relevant learning options.</p>
            <p>We understand that getting into Finnish language and culture can be hard and often frustrating, with a lot of barriers to overcome. We want to make this part of the process easy for you. If we succeed, this website will serve just like the menu you open at your favorite restaurant. Please get comfortable, look through it and pick your dish for today!</p>
